    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as it should, providing a reliable driving experience. While there are some minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with regular use, such as small paint chips and light wear on the upholstery, the interior is clean and all electronics are fully functional. This is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
