      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been curated to exacting standards, exhibiting a level of preservation that rivals its original showroom state. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail reflects an uncompromising commitment to excellence. For the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a pristine asset maintained in peerless condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
